<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">

    <title>성공하자!</title>
    <style>
        h1 {
            text-align: center;
            color: white;
        }

        header {
            padding: 2px;
            background-color: rgb(190, 228, 238);
            margin: 0;
            top: 0;
            box-shadow: 3px 3px 3px lightgrey;
        }

        p#logout button {
            background-color: white;
            color: skyblue;
            border-radius: 3px;
            width: 150px;
            height: 40px;
            margin-right: 30px;
            display: inline;
        }

        p#logout {
            text-align: right;
        }

        .sidenav {
            height: 100%;
            width: 160px;
            position: fixed;
            left: 7px;
            background-color: white;
            overflow-x: hidden;
            margin-top: 10px;
            border: rgb(190, 228, 238) 2px solid;
            border-radius: 3px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        nav ul li p a {
            text-align: center;
            text-decoration: none;
        }

        nav ul li:nth-child(2n) p a {
            background-color: lightblue;
            color: white;
        }

        nav ul li:nth-child(2n) p a:link {
            background-color: lightblue;
            color: white;
        }

        nav ul li:nth-child(2n) p a:hover {
            background-color: white;
            color: rgb(74, 113, 145);
            font-weight: 700;
        }

        nav ul li:nth-child(2n-1) p a {
            color: rgb(74, 113, 145);
        }

        nav ul li:nth-child(2n-1) p a:link {
            color: rgb(74, 113, 145);
        }

        nav ul li:nth-child(2n-1) p a:hover {
            color: white;
            background-color: lightblue;
        }

        #contents {
            overflow: auto;
            text-align: center;
            border: 1px rgb(191, 210, 212) solid;
            margin: 10px 0px 40px 180px;
            height: 600px;
        }

        #infor {
            position: relative;
            left: 40%;
            top: 10%;

        }

        #infor table,
        #infor tr,
        #infor td {
            border: solid 1px black;
            letter-spacing: 5px;
            line-height: 1.7;
        }
    </style>
    <script>
        function logOut() {
            window.location.href = '/';
        }
    </script>
    <header>
        <h1>
            금오공과대학교 수강신청 페이지에 오신 것을 환영합니다!
        </h1>
        <p id="logout">
            <button onclick="logOut()">logout</button>
        </p>
    </header>
    <nav class="sidenav">
        <ul style="list-style-type: none;">
            <li>
